textBeforeTable: Comments: Homepage source content will be stored in directory called website in each project repository. During the move, write-access will not be possible. Between Saturday the 11th afternoon and Sunday the 12th, homepages code repositories will move from CVS to SVN. Item posted by Mathieu Roy <yeupou> on Fri 10 Nov 2006 09:45:52 AM UTC.
